Attributes.description: Etiology, pathophysiology, and nutrition therapy for selected diseases and conditions. Topics include metabolism, obesity, eating disorders, diabetes, hypertension, and cardiovascular disease. Restricted to students in year 3 of the dietetics major.
Attributes.prereq: Pre-reqs: All of FNH 350, FNH 370 and one of BIOL 153, BIOL 155.
